OL,3,CRachel Reeves insists welfare reforms
OL,4,Cwill 'lift people out of poverty'
OL,6,FThe chancellor says negative impact
OL,7,Fassessments of the reforms she
OL,8,Fannounced on Wednesday are based on a
OL,9,Ffalse premise
OL,11,FRachel Reeves has denied the cuts to
OL,12,Fwelfare announced in her Spring
OL,13,FStatement will make people worse off.
OL,15,FThe chancellor insisted assessments of
OL,16,Fher Spring Statement were based on a
OL,17,Ffalse premise that "no one will go
OL,18,Fback into work."
