OL,3,CRachel Reeves insists welfare reforms
OL,4,Cwill 'lift people out of poverty'
OL,6,FShe said the whole point of these
OL,7,Fgovernment reforms is to move people
OL,8,Foff benefits and into work.
OL,10,F"We want to lift people out of poverty
OL,11,Fand give more people the opportunity
OL,12,Fto make a career," the chancellor said.
OL,14,F"I came into politics to give more
OL,15,Fpeople a decent start in life because
OL,16,Fof my experience growing up in the 80s
OL,17,Fand 90s."
