OL,3,CRachel Reeves insists welfare reforms
OL,4,Cwill 'lift people out of poverty'
OL,6,FAs part of her Spring Statement,
OL,7,FReeves revealed changes to Personal
OL,8,Findependence payments (Pip) and
OL,9,Funiversal credit, along with #500
OL,10,Fmillion of extra cuts to incapacity
OL,11,Fbenefit.
OL,13,FAlthough Reeves said the Spring
OL,14,FStatement means "people will be on
OL,15,Faverage over #500 a year better off
OL,16,Funder this Labour government," the
OL,17,Fforecast looks different for those set
OL,18,Fto lose out in welfare cuts.
