OL,3,CRachel Reeves insists welfare reforms
OL,4,Cwill 'lift people out of poverty'
OL,6,FThey say this is the result of a
OL,7,Fcombination of a weak economic outlook
OL,8,Fand benefit cuts that fall
OL,9,Fdisproportionately on lower-income
OL,10,Ffamilies.
OL,12,F"The outlook for living standards
OL,13,Fremains bleak," said Ruth Curtice, the
OL,14,Fthink tank's chief executive.
OL,16,FShortly after Reeves' Spring
OL,17,FStatement, Trump announced 25% tariffs
OL,18,Fon all cars built outside of the US.
OL,19,FThese tariffs have the potential to be
OL,20,Fa hammer blow to Reeves' already tight
OL,21,Ffiscal headroom.
